32:15.367 --> 32:17.169
not emotional.

32:17.203 --> 32:18.437
Kids say that
molestation hurts.

32:18.470 --> 32:20.406
Emma called it a sin.

32:20.439 --> 32:22.174
What do you think
about those pictures?

32:22.208 --> 32:24.476
Well, a lot of doctors
recommend massage
for children under stress.

32:24.510 --> 32:27.479
I would prescribe it for Emma,
if she were my patient.

32:27.513 --> 32:29.048
How do you explain
Emma's allegations?

32:29.081 --> 32:31.350
Parental
Alienation Syndrome.

32:31.383 --> 32:33.452
I thought P.A.S. was
when a couple splits up

32:33.485 --> 32:36.488
and the mom brainwashes
the kids into thinking
that dad's a bastard.

32:36.522 --> 32:37.689
Well, the same thing's
happening here,

32:37.723 --> 32:40.159
except that
it's the grandmother
turning Emma against Zoe.

32:40.192 --> 32:42.194
But why would Emma
go along with it?

32:42.228 --> 32:45.364
Her grandmother's
manipulated her into
believing that it's true.

32:45.397 --> 32:47.433
So she used the massages
to convince Emma

32:47.466 --> 32:49.401
