something awful.

32:49.435 --> 32:53.172
It's emotional abuse inflicted
by her loving grandmother.

32:53.205 --> 32:54.306
At the very least,

32:54.340 --> 32:55.541
it's custodial interference.

32:55.574 --> 32:57.243
At most,
reckless endangerment.

32:57.276 --> 32:59.778
Either way, the grandparents
still only get
a slap on the wrist.

32:59.811 --> 33:01.480
Unless we can prove
unlawful imprisonment.

33:01.513 --> 33:03.715
How?

33:03.749 --> 33:06.352
Well, they kept a little girl
away from her rightful home

33:06.385 --> 33:08.087
