is because Zoe's gay.

33:10.122 --> 33:12.458
Which would make it
a hate crime.

33:12.491 --> 33:13.592
It's a D felony.

33:13.625 --> 33:15.327
They could get seven years.

33:17.663 --> 33:19.465
Arrest them.

33:22.268 --> 33:25.637
Oliver and Deborah Boyd,
you're under arrest
for unlawful imprisonment.

33:25.671 --> 33:27.273
What are you
talking about?

33:27.306 --> 33:29.275
You filled Emma's head
with lies

33:29.308 --> 33:30.309
to keep her away
from her mother.

33:30.342 --> 33:32.478
Her mother is dead.

33:32.511 --> 33:34.580
Zoe is ruining
my granddaughter's life.

33:34.613 --> 33:36.748
It's our moral duty
to protect her.

33:36.782 --> 33:38.450
Well, try following
the Eighth Commandment.

33:38.484 --> 33:40.352
Thou shall not bear
false witness.

33:43.689 --> 33:45.491
(Zoe)
