just died.

34:01.573 --> 34:03.442
It's understandable
that she'd be upset.

34:03.475 --> 34:07.379
It's not the only reason.
She's scared.

34:07.413 --> 34:08.680
The other night
she woke up crying.

34:08.714 --> 34:13.252
She dreamed
her mom had died,

34:13.285 --> 34:16.755
and the police had come
to take me to jail.

34:16.788 --> 34:18.490
And she kept
calling out for me.

34:18.524 --> 34:19.858
But I couldn't hear her.

34:19.891 --> 34:24.330
No one could hear her.

34:24.363 --> 34:26.265
Thank you.

34:30.369 --> 34:33.805
How long has Emma
been in therapy?
About six months.

34:33.839 --> 34:38.210
Since the kids at school
started making fun of her
for having two moms.

34:38.244 --> 34:41.847
