St. Victor's for three years.
Why suddenly a problem?

34:41.880 --> 34:45.484
No one knew about her home
situation until recently.

34:45.517 --> 34:47.786
When you insisted on making
your presence known at school.

34:47.819 --> 34:49.688
(Zoe)
Kate was sick.

34:49.721 --> 34:51.457
Emma needed a parent
for school functions.

34:51.490 --> 34:53.225
And you needed
to make a point...

34:53.259 --> 34:55.461
that you were gay

34:55.494 --> 34:57.596
and the school
better not discriminate you.

34:57.629 --> 34:59.731
(Zoe)
I didn't think the school
would react the way they did.

34:59.765 --> 35:01.867
But when they got angry
at your lie,

35:01.900 --> 35:04.436
you chose to
take them to court.

35:04.470 --> 35:06.438
It was important
to take a stand.

35:06.472 --> 35:08.207
More important
than Emma's happiness.

35:08.240 --> 35:10.176
No, of course not.

35:10.209 --> 35:12.911
He was so miserable
at St. Victor's.

35:12.944 --> 35:15.614
Why not enroll her
in another school?

35:15.647 --> 35:20.219
I didn't want her to be ashamed
