35:36.635 --> 35:40.172
And because of you Sean Hamill
will never walk again.

35:40.206 --> 35:41.740
Objection.

35:41.773 --> 35:43.442
I know.

35:43.475 --> 35:47.313
I'd change it if I could.

35:47.346 --> 35:51.550
I made a mistake,
and I'm sorry.

35:53.619 --> 35:55.921
Nothing further.

36:05.297 --> 36:07.333
Even after
her mom got sick,

36:07.366 --> 36:09.868
Emma was always
a happy girl.

36:09.901 --> 36:13.905
And then suddenly
about eight months ago...

36:13.939 --> 36:14.973
