36:18.744 --> 36:19.878
and lonely.

36:19.911 --> 36:20.912
Zoe was either at work

36:20.946 --> 36:23.615
or at the hospital.

36:23.649 --> 36:25.984
Emma's brother had to walk
her home from school everyday.

36:26.017 --> 36:28.487
What did you do?

36:28.520 --> 36:32.358
