asked our daughter if Emma
could stay with us after school.

36:32.391 --> 36:34.826
Zoe didn't like it.

36:34.860 --> 36:39.765
That's when she made Kate
write her will.

36:39.798 --> 36:43.402
She made Kate
write her will?

36:43.435 --> 36:45.371
Kate was getting sicker
and sicker,

36:45.404 --> 36:46.838
and sometimes she didn't
even recognize us.

36:46.872 --> 36:50.642
Zoe wanted to make sure
she got sole custody of Emma.

36:50.676 --> 36:53.379
Mrs. Boyd,
did you persuade Emma

36:53.412 --> 36:54.613
to make false allegations
against Zoe?

36:54.646 --> 36:57.449
No.

36:57.483 --> 37:01.587
I saw Emma was unhappy,
and I asked her what was wrong.

37:01.620 --> 37:02.988
That's all.

37:03.021 --> 37:04.590
Thank you.

37:07.759 --> 37:09.628
Mrs. Boyd,

37:09.661 --> 37:11.963
can you read the signature
at the bottom
of your daughter's will,

37:11.997 --> 37:13.965
right next to where
it says "witness"?

37:13.999 --> 37:16.402
Ray Monaghan.

37:16.435 --> 37:20.906
So Kate's ex-husband
thought she was lucid enough
to co-sign her will.

37:20.939 --> 37:22.541
Kate wasn't thinking clearly.

37:22.574 --> 37:24.876
She-- She didn't
want to hurt Zoe.

37:24.910 --> 37:27.279
She wasn't thinking
of the best home for Emma.

37:27.313 --> 37:29.515
By the best home, do you mean
the best heterosexual home?

37:29.548 --> 37:31.550
Objection.
Argumentative.

37:31.583 --> 37:33.552
