37:33.585 --> 37:36.021
Do you think gay people
should be allowed
to raise children?

37:37.723 --> 37:39.491
Ideally, no.

37:39.525 --> 37:43.028
I think children should be
raised by their father
and their mother.

37:43.061 --> 37:46.532
This is why you made up
allegations
against Zoe Dunlop,

37:46.565 --> 37:48.934
because your faith
rejected the idea

37:48.967 --> 37:50.702
of a gay woman raising
your granddaughter.

37:50.736 --> 37:52.904
It isn't just about faith.

37:52.938 --> 37:55.341
