what would happen to Emma
if Zoe raises her.

37:55.374 --> 37:56.742
(Novak)
What would happen?

37:56.775 --> 38:00.612
(Deb)
She will grow up

38:00.646 --> 38:02.414
sexually confused,
promiscuous.

38:02.448 --> 38:04.850
She will experiment
with homosexual relationships.

38:04.883 --> 38:06.752
