think that?

38:06.785 --> 38:09.087
I have read studies.

38:09.120 --> 38:14.860
Like the one that says
that kids raised by gay couples

38:14.893 --> 38:17.829
are 48 times more likely
to be molested by their parents

38:17.863 --> 38:20.632
than kids raised
by straight parents.

38:20.666 --> 38:22.834
Where did you come across
these studies?

38:22.868 --> 38:24.736
My attorney showed them
to me.

38:30.108 --> 38:32.478
When did he
show them to you?

38:32.511 --> 38:34.546
Objection.
Relevance?

38:34.580 --> 38:37.315
Please answer the question,
Mrs. Boyd.

38:39.785 --> 38:42.654
During Emma's trial
in family court.

38:42.688 --> 38:46.091
So, just before
you accused Zoe Dunlop
of molesting Emma.

38:46.124 --> 38:47.793
Yes.

38:47.826 --> 38:51.430
What I read made me
start looking for clues.

38:51.463 --> 38:52.664
Then when we found the photos,

38:52.698 --> 38:55.100
