can't prove any of it.

40:07.506 --> 40:09.140
Mr. Decker,

40:09.174 --> 40:12.077
at the very least this
is a serious breach
of ethical conduct.

40:12.110 --> 40:14.045
Your Honor--

40:14.079 --> 40:16.748
