but to remove you as counsel
and declare a mistrial.

40:23.088 --> 40:25.457
I'm willing to offer you
a plea arrangement

40:25.491 --> 40:28.126
in exchange for your testimony
against Mr. Decker.

40:28.159 --> 40:29.861
Why would we testify
against him?

40:29.895 --> 40:33.799
Because he manipulated you
by using faulty research.

40:33.832 --> 40:37.135
According to the American
Sociological Association,

40:37.168 --> 40:39.471
gay parents are not...

40:39.505 --> 40:42.608
48 times more likely
to molest their kids.

40:45.511 --> 40:47.846
The article I read
says differently.

40:47.879 --> 40:50.849
That article was written
by a man who was expelled

40:50.882 --> 40:52.851
by the American
Psychological Association

40:52.884 --> 40:55.854
for misrepresenting
statistics.

40:55.887 --> 40:57.956
The American Academy
of Pediatrics

40:57.989 --> 41:00.892
and The National Association
of Social Workers both agree

41:00.926 --> 41:02.894
that kids raised
in gay homes
are just as healthy

41:02.928 --> 41:04.930
as kids raised
in straight homes.

41:04.963 --> 41:07.265
Why would Mr. Decker
lie to us?

41:07.298 --> 41:09.701
To further his agenda.

41:09.735 --> 41:12.137
He wanted to use you
and Emma as an example...

41:12.170 --> 41:14.039
the damage homosexuality
is doing to society.

41:16.141 --> 41:18.877
All we wanted
was to protect Emma.

41:18.910 --> 41:20.178
