41:20.211 --> 41:21.880
(Benson)
Casey.

41:21.913 --> 41:24.616
Zoe wants to speak
to you.

41:24.650 --> 41:27.152
Emma, why don't we
wait outside, okay?

41:31.256 --> 41:33.625
I wanna know
why they're here.

41:33.659 --> 41:35.627
We're gonna testify
against Mr. Decker.

41:35.661 --> 41:37.696
Zoe, we're so sorry.

41:37.729 --> 41:40.098
We were only trying
to do what we thought
was best for Emma.

41:40.131 --> 41:43.101
I don't believe you.

41:43.134 --> 41:45.637
James Decker
took advantage of them...

41:45.671 --> 41:47.305
the same way
he took advantage of Emma.

41:47.338 --> 41:50.876
I know it would be hard
to forgive them.

41:50.909 --> 41:52.644
It's not going to happen.

41:52.678 --> 41:56.081
Zoe, please.

41:58.717 --> 42:00.518
She's my granddaughter.

42:01.920 --> 42:04.022
And she's my daughter.

42:04.055 --> 42:06.157
You turned my baby
against me.

42:07.659 --> 42:10.261
You convinced her
I was a child molester.

42:11.897 --> 42:14.199
